OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's farm has
OL,4,Ctuberculosis - but what is bovine TB?
OL,6,FJeremy Clarkson has announced that his
OL,7,Ffarm has "gone down with TB".
OL,9,FThe former Top Gear host has run his
OL,10,Fown farm - Diddly Squat - in Chipping
OL,11,FNorton, Oxfordshire, since 2008.
OL,13,FThe farm is also the set of his
OL,14,Fdocumentary series Clarkson's Farm,
OL,15,Fwhich first aired in 2021.
OL,17,FClarkson highlighted that it was
OL,18,Fbovine TB, saying on X: "It doesn't
OL,19,Faffect people, just our poor cows."
