OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's farm has
OL,4,Ctuberculosis - but what is bovine TB?
OL,6,F"Everyone here is absolutely
OL,7,Fdevastated," he added.
OL,9,FSo what is TB, and can it impact
OL,10,Fhumans?
OL,12,FWhat is bovine TB?
OL,14,FTB - short for tuberculosis - is an
OL,15,Finfection that typically affects the
OL,16,Flungs. Bovine TB is a chronic disease
OL,17,Fthat can affect most mammals.
