OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's farm has
OL,4,Ctuberculosis - but what is bovine TB?
OL,6,FCattle can pass TB onto one another,
OL,7,Fbut it can also spread through direct
OL,8,For indirect contact with infected
OL,9,Fbadgers.
OL,11,FIndirect contact is possible through
OL,12,Fcontact with bodily fluids and faeces.
OL,14,FCan humans catch it?
OL,16,FHumans can catch bovine TB, but the
OL,17,Frisk of infection is very low for the
OL,18,Fvast majority of the population.
