OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's farm has
OL,4,Ctuberculosis - but what is bovine TB?
OL,6,FIt is possible to catch the disease
OL,7,Fthrough unpasteurised dairy products
OL,8,Ffrom an infected animal, inhaling
OL,9,Fbacteria exhaled by the animals, or
OL,10,Finhaling bacteria from the carcasses
OL,11,Fof infected animals or their excrement.
OL,13,FIs it a problem for farmers?
OL,15,FBovine TB can have a big impact on
OL,16,Ffarmers and their farms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
