OL,4,Ctuberculosis - but what is bovine TB?
OL,6,FCattle should regularly be tested for
OL,7,FTB, as often as every six months if
OL,8,Fthe farm is in an area deemed "high-
OL,9,Frisk" for the disease, and that
OL,10,Fprocess can be time-consuming and
OL,11,Fexpensive.
OL,13,FIf animals do test positive, it can
OL,14,Fhave huge emotional and financial
OL,15,Fimpacts on the farmers, as well as
OL,16,Fposing a risk to other livestock.
