OL,3,CJeremy Clarkson's farm has
OL,4,Ctuberculosis - but what is bovine TB?
OL,6,FAnimals that test positive for TB or
OL,7,Fhave had direct contact with a
OL,8,Fpositive animal tend to be slaughtered.
OL,10,FThis is to prevent the disease from
OL,11,Fspreading further.
OL,13,FFarmers can then claim compensation
OL,14,Ffor their animals if they comply with
OL,15,FThe Cattle Identification Regulations
OL,16,F2007.
